openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: refComponent
  description: refComponent
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.{host}.io/v1
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      host:
        default: openapi
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider
  - url: https://{subdomain}.swagger.io:{port}/{basePath}
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      subdomain:
        default: petstore
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider
      port:
        enum:
          - '8443'
          - '443'
        default: '443'
      basePath:
        default: v2
paths:
  /pets:
    post:
      summary: Creates a new pets.
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: html
components: {}
